{"tid":1751024,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"用父子關係類比政府人民，呢個係古代皇權用以控制人民嘅手段","createTime":"2019-11-24T15:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T05:49:13.000Z","uid":64744,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"53e9d9a01b37744bcbd5160094c949a301c2c228","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"原post:<br />\n我老母send左幅咁既圖，點拆？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1750925\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1750925</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個叫中國式邏輯，三綱五常：<br />\n君為臣綱，父為子綱，夫為妻綱<br />\n<br />\n用父子關係類比君臣，目的係為咗正當化君權<br />\n唔係我9up，提出嗰個仆街董仲舒(漢代)本身嘅目的就係維護政治制度，為君主制度服務。<br />\n<br />\n如果你用現代嘅民主制度去睇，用父子關係類比君臣係完全唔合常理。<br />\n<br />\n因為政府唔係你老豆、<br />\n因為你唔係唔聽話嘅小朋友，你係有獨立思考能力嘅人、<br />\n因為人民有人權不服從社會/政府不公義的制度。"},{"pid":"f71cde79f76efaec368cd547f5d600bd9b700009","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:25:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4686cb1139ce340750a19679d37999e620846e7","tid":1751024,"uid":171849,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"自由民主係基本人權<br />\n講咩民主可唔可以當飯食既人<br />\n你地同豬冇分別"},{"pid":"74e089f259a184fcf53bd7d3f169e25e2d081087","tid":1751024,"uid":175346,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15ccf74e5f4c11824aeed2f5298b72970dfbf354","tid":1751024,"uid":271250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，父母係俾錢個細路養住佢，所以細路聽父母話都算合理；但政府唔係俾錢市民，係調返轉市民俾錢政府，所以政府聽市民話先合理（當然點樣聽呀，好多市民㗎喎點綜合意見呀，呢啲就容後再說）"},{"pid":"9adcb5e7436ef278990e224af1996ad08f8f0986","tid":1751024,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aece2d7a45d7acc9807777eea0f55fb7d67094","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5fc8535840d91c763a9c650f65c086137be1fcc9","tid":1751024,"uid":91783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74e089f259a184fcf53bd7d3f169e25e2d081087","tid":1751024,"uid":175346,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"無錯，政府既權力係來自人民<br />\n邊個係莊邊係先係閒要分清楚"},{"pid":"e605a4158b23d12639741878284713a2a4e3ef7e","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"讀春秋孔子嘅儒家，<br />\n唔好學被皇權閹割既偽儒家。"},{"pid":"48f094a9a9a17b241ce91154824784e5c5664d52","tid":1751024,"uid":51698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:34:05.000Z","msg":"唔明點解啲藍絲咁鐘意認人做老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621e771883c0a84f8036230600a9d612a0fe878e","tid":1751024,"uid":253693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"應該老豆先係人民"},{"pid":"f13bea1efcad565df57df730092937b20a1dd708","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"Wiki：<br />\n孔子從沒要求「君要臣死，臣不得不死；父要子亡，子不得不亡」[4]，孔子有言：「君使臣以禮，臣事君以忠」[5]，「士有諍友，則身不離於令名；父有諍子，則身不陷於不義。故當不義，則子不可以不諍於父，臣不可以不諍於君。故當不義，則諍之，從父之令，又焉得為孝乎？」[6]。孟子則更進一步闡述：「君之視臣如手足，則臣視君如腹心；君之視臣如犬馬，則臣視君如國人；君之視臣如土芥，則臣視君如寇讎。」[7]"},{"pid":"e5f955aabf8a3f973bde4c504722b9508804dfc3","tid":1751024,"uid":64744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966fd4d595e73037c45f8ccc938683afcb4b5c38","tid":1751024,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意打老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78554054ab545d0085c313dd9e54fe4ebf20